<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulrich Amman zu Kelheim</head><p>Der Rat teilt Unkenntnis von einem Streit mit einem Bürger zu Nürnberg mit, gewährt Amman aber bis zum Palmtag Geleit wegen Austrags.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_86" id="42v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_86_r2l20"><expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Amman <expan>geſeʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü Kelheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_86_r2l21">Lieber <expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns aber <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l22">brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / . Nu habt Jr vns aber keinen der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> benant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l23">So wiſſen wir ſelber von der ſache nichts <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wen es antriffet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l24">Vnd wiſſen auch cʒü der cʒeit nichts des wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr knecht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l25">beſchuldıgen <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mit ew <expan>cʒeſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dann lıeb vnd güt / . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l26">Wolt Jr aber <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü vns <expan>reit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / wenn Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hıecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l31">vnd <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>nehſte<ex>n</ex></expan> palmtag cʒü vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_86_line_1576532992331_1035">vnd ew des <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> wöllet / So ſüllet Jr vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l32">die mit ew reiten vnſer ſlechts geleitte <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒü vns vnd <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r2l33">vns <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Remi<ex>ni</ex>ſce<ex>re</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_86" id="42v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Amman, <expan>gesezze<ex>n</ex></expan> czü
                        Kelheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns aber
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt,
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>. Nu habt ir uns aber keinen
                        der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> benant, so wissen wir selber von der
                        sache nichts <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wen es antriffet und wissen auch
                        czü der czeit nichts, des wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr knecht
                        beschuldigen <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mit ew
                            <expan>czeschicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dann lieb und güt. Wolt ir aber
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> czü uns <expan>reit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wenn
                        ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>nehste<ex>n</ex></expan> palmtag</q>16.03.1410</note></app> czü uns
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>und ew des <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> wöllet,
                        so süllet ir und die mit ew reiten unser slechts geleitte
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czü uns und
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> uns
                            <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>remi<ex>ni</ex>sce<ex>re</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
